Package: sensortowerR
Title: R Interface to Sensor Tower API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Peter", "Black", , "pblack@gameeconomistconsulting.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a clean interface to the Sensor Tower API for mobile app analytics.
    Fetches and processes key performance indicators (KPIs) including revenue, downloads,
    and active users at different time granularities.
